    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/7efb06d676c2283ac6e5916f538c3c8c.poster.avif?t=1732018555\" width=800 height=553 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/7efb06d676c2283ac6e5916f538c3c8c.webm?t=1732018555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/9251044a807a698b233722c9ca897d5b.poster.avif?t=1732018555\" width=800 height=552 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/9251044a807a698b233722c9ca897d5b.webm?t=1732018555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/9251044a807a698b233722c9ca897d5b.mp4?t=1732018555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/e4e4688f81a451672a887ef32917dce6.poster.avif?t=1732018555\" width=800 height=553 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/e4e4688f81a451672a887ef32917dce6.webm?t=1732018555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Px2d》外置动作库下载地址：<u></u></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【Px2d】是一款专门制作2d像素角色动画的帧动画编辑器。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持4方向角色制作。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Px2d】的三大优势。 <br>优势1、无需绘画，即可创造自己的角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >区别于传统的像素绘画工具，要先自己绘制角色，然后在制作角色动画。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在【Px2d】里你不需要绘画，无需任何的绘画经验。即可创造自己的角色。【Px2d】依托于庞大的素材库，在素材库中，有大量的素材供用户选择，只需挑选自己喜欢的素材，就可以创造自己的角色了。 随心所欲，定制属于你的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 支持导入自定义素材 <br>除了素材库中的素材，【Px2d】也支持用户导入自己的素材制作动画。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>优势2、告别单一模板，创造无限可能</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >区别于传统的纸娃娃系统，只有一种单一固定的动作模板。因为动作是固定的，无法调节，无法满足我们对动作的需求。 <br>【Px2d】采用了角色身体组件化模式。角色身体的每一个部位都是一个组件。可以随意调节。这样就可以最大程度的满足我们动作的需求。想要什么动作，就可以自己摆什么动作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>【Px2d】2.0版升级了内置动作库，内置82种动作。包含了战斗类动作和生活类动作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/f0c3a5f30400f506c8817f1b2b55fa6b.poster.avif?t=1732018555\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/f0c3a5f30400f506c8817f1b2b55fa6b.webm?t=1732018555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/f0c3a5f30400f506c8817f1b2b55fa6b.mp4?t=1732018555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/55268b21b60d8b849fa05752850fd2e2.poster.avif?t=1732018555\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/55268b21b60d8b849fa05752850fd2e2.webm?t=1732018555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/55268b21b60d8b849fa05752850fd2e2.mp4?t=1732018555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 优势3、一键导出，大大的提高效率</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Px2d】支持一键导出png格式图片。无论你对角色样式，还是角色动作做了任何的修改，只需一键，即可导出资源。</p>",
